Package: datamaps
Title: Create Interactive Web Maps with the JavaScript 'Datamaps' Library
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("John", "Coene", email = "jcoenep@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Created and customise interactive choropleth maps, and add overlay arcs, or bubbles. 
    These maps can be used directly from the R console, from 'RStudio', in Shiny apps with proxies 
    and R Markdown documents.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
